      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nI happy with a different patch to set the tunable from DLC.\n\nNote that I will rename LNET_MAX_INTERFACES here to LNET_MAX_INTERFACES_DEFAULT or something like that. The reason is that I just removed LNET_MAX_INTERFACES, and would be re-introducing something with the same name but different semantics, and with a much larger value. I'd rather have things set up so the compiler can catch it if someone overlooks this change.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 3
    },
